{"tid":604291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【舊聞】司徒華：邊個會受歷史審判，大家放長時間睇","createTime":"2018-03-24T14:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T09:40:28.000Z","uid":72730,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ef1c12051a6323a82c0c99df7253ed800b4f66ad","tid":604291,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T14:21:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">司徒華被擲陰司紙</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/221912_829f5a3a756932ede220aca153d7de53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F221912_829f5a3a756932ede220aca153d7de53.jpg&h=67fb39bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有遊行人士自製標語力撐司徒華。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】正抗癌的民主黨元老司徒華昨日坐輪椅出席遊行，其間一度遭市民狙擊，遊行出發前被擲「陰司紙」，華叔一度與不滿民主黨的市民舌戰。表明早有心理準備遭個別市民咒罵的華叔，坦言只會對挑釁一笑置之，「佢哋咁做，只會激勵我更加堅定，佢哋講嘅嘢都冇道理，我何必嬲呢？」華叔接受訪問時，<span style=\"color: red;\">有市民指控民主黨出賣港人，華叔即場反問該市民：「賣咗你？賣咗你幾多錢？你係豬係狗，畀人賣 o架？」</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>「激起更高昂嘅鬥志」</strong><br />\n剛展開電療抗癌的華叔昨午在義工陪同下，在遊行前半小時坐輪椅抵達維園，並遊行至富豪酒店才乘車離開。華叔出發前，有市民高舉「民主黨出賣港人」標語抗議，華叔則在民陣帳篷下接受訪問。<span style=\"color: red;\">華叔指，質疑民主黨出賣民主的人，「政治智慧同政治道德都唔夠水平」</span>，因為民調顯示逾六成市民支持該黨提出的改良方案，又指民主黨與中央「枱底交易」的指控無證據，「係屬於誹謗」。<br />\n有向民主黨抗議的市民對華叔高喊「祝你早日康復！」華叔即說：「多謝你嘅祝福。」怎料<span style=\"color: red;\">該市民說：「我唔係祝福你，我係期望你受歷史嘅教訓同審判。」華叔聞言後未有動氣，只說：「邊個會受歷史審判，大家放長時間睇。」</span>華叔事後稱，不會因個別無理指控感到不快，「佢哋咁做，只會激起我哋更高昂嘅鬥志」。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報<br />\n2010年07月02日<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20100702&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=14196122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20100702%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D14196122&d=ZU2mIAMeqG50Epqbz%2BTAa4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b7923b84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20100702%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D14196122&h=fb3131dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20100702&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=14196122</a>"},{"pid":"15e2a1e94185d855a5020325b317db99210ef2a7","tid":604291,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f5ff8e8bbd2104d13af5c9596c6ecc3c0c8cfd","tid":604291,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15e2a1e94185d855a5020325b317db99210ef2a7","tid":604291,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T17:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係慧侵師太, 記唔記得我呀"},{"pid":"65339450ede11c3179261a4bf56ae06b3333ed16","tid":604291,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T17:43:00.000Z","msg":"地下共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39d6f44240e2e70a4c8982f61b6cb0587d924e6","tid":604291,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32f5ff8e8bbd2104d13af5c9596c6ecc3c0c8cfd","tid":604291,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15e2a1e94185d855a5020325b317db99210ef2a7","tid":604291,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T17:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係慧侵師太, 記唔記得我呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T17:45:00.000Z","msg":"緊係記得<br />\n幫你出過post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994e81cf82949606936d7477da719407b83f944d","tid":604291,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f39d6f44240e2e70a4c8982f61b6cb0587d924e6","tid":604291,"uid":47359,"like":0,"di